We've found that abortion pills are available in every state from:&nbsp;&nbsp;

- Online clinics that mail pills
- In-person clinics (only in some states)&nbsp;&nbsp;
- Websites that sell pills&nbsp;&nbsp;
- Community networks that mail pills&nbsp;&nbsp;

Our {% inlineLink action={discriminant: "anchor", value: "top"} _language="" %}guide{% /inlineLink %} shares research on all of these options. Depending where you live, accessing abortion pills online may come with {% inlineLink action={discriminant: "popup", value: "medically-safe-possible-legal-risk"} _language="" %}legal risk{% /inlineLink %}.
